      "text": "* ''Observe and interact'': By taking time to engage with nature we can design solutions that suit our particular situation.\n* ''Catch and store energy'': By developing systems that collect resources at peak abundance, we can use them in times of need."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "d5a78456-6995-4e68-a51a-897177574dcd",
      "text": "# ''Obtain a yield'': Ensure that you are getting truly useful rewards as part of the work that you are doing."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "5336e04b-83d1-40e7-bea8-8840d5830b19",
      "text": "# ''Apply self-regulation and accept feedback'': We need to discourage inappropriate activity to ensure that systems can continue to function well."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "98be4844-d800-4665-98bb-77120d0f3801",
      "text": "# ''Use and value [[renewable]] resources and services'': Make the best use of nature's abundance to reduce our consumptive behavior and dependence on non-renewable resources."
