      "text": "# ''Integrate rather than segregate'': By putting the right things in the right place, relationships develop between those things and they work together to support each other."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f07eb1fc-b2ee-4c1b-9e66-ae390731ae18",
      "text": "# ''Use small and slow solutions'': Small and slow systems are easier to maintain than big ones, making better use of local resources and producing more sustainable outcomes."
    },
